Natives of Cathrys, vaaths are vicious, sadistic killers. They cause pain and suffering not because they need to, but because they delight in it.
Physically, theyÂ  quadrupeds with characteristics of both insects and reptiles. They have whiplike snouts, and their bodies are protected by chitinous shells.
